{"tid":913083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國領事館遇襲】巴基斯坦分離組織認責　斥中國「剝奪資源」","createTime":"2018-11-23T06:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T11:18:10.000Z","uid":75969,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"087c1f3dee64ebe9d59fe2b6b4c9d35777c82af2","tid":913083,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181123/s00005/77a77c35f494e44a226ed69f7cd563c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181123%2Fs00005%2F77a77c35f494e44a226ed69f7cd563c8.jpg&h=be5927ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐巴基斯坦卡拉奇領事館周五（23日）遇襲，兩名警員殉職，另有領事館保安受傷。綜合路透社及法新社報道，巴基斯坦分離組織「俾路支解放軍」（Balochistan Liberation Army，BLA）承認責任，指中國「剝奪我們的資源」。一個聲稱是該組織官方Twitter帳戶，發放3名男子舉起「V字」手勢的照片，稱該組織「襲擊了卡拉奇的中國領事館」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181123/s00005/77a69e55a565c21966bdfab53f1182f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181123%2Fs00005%2F77a69e55a565c21966bdfab53f1182f2.jpg&h=ab0b4c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n領事館於當地時間早上約9時半遇襲，路透社引述卡拉奇警方稱，3名施襲者企圖闖入簽證區，全部被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n中新網報道，領事館外交人員目前安全。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/法新社/中新網/海外網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181123/s00005/1542953037556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181123%2Fs00005%2F1542953037556&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2Btq54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c9ea05ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181123%2Fs00005%2F1542953037556&h=21ba724d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181123/s00005/1542953037556</a>"},{"pid":"5538d35d45e8918340207d9d5ef9a8990d7d9071","tid":913083,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:56:55.000Z"